    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or use. Every feature and electronic component functions perfectly, and the engine bay is spotless. It has been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, making it a perfect example for a discerning collector or enthusiast.",
